## 7. Key Takeaways

- Social engineering targets humans not systems
- Psychological manipulation is more effective than technical attacks
- No amount of technology fully protects against human error
- Education and awareness are the most powerful defences
- Verification procedures and a healthy scepticism are essential
- Nepal faces significant and growing social engineering threats
  that require trained professionals to address

